:0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d62f47c15773632923534a69503dd47ac95706f5","tid":805503,"uid":64303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:25:27.000Z","msg":"有咩推介 成日睇睇下咸片轉左4g"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"Router路由器 集中討論區(7)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/766417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/766417</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"69c893f92dd14b7d524f56ce647b43dbd5c20fc9","tid":805503,"uid":171800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8548fc06375cb7b44b75f0e0c615bb481aad41b8","tid":805503,"uid":99742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:43:04.000Z","msg":"我都有同樣問題, <br />\n會無端端上唔到網, <br />\n成屋所有device都係連到Wifi,  但上唔到網。<br />\n之後要熄router 再開返先得。<br />\n<br />\n其實係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T02:54:28.000Z","msg":"Iphone開飛行模 再關就得"},{"pid":"3c1b94906c853d7e306e2ad65f05d2f0d2e5c102","tid":805503,"uid":194130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8548fc06375cb7b44b75f0e0c615bb481aad41b8","tid":805503,"uid":99742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T01:43:04.000Z","msg":"我都有同樣問題, <br />\n會無端端上唔到網, <br />\n成屋所有device都係連到Wifi,  但上唔到網。<br />\n之後要熄router 再開返先得。<br />\n<br />\n其實係點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:27:24.000Z","msg":"其實咁未必係router問題<br />\nrouter只係一個點你必需要經過<br />\n連到Wifi即係你既設備連去router冇問題<br />\n但router出唔到街<br />\n只有一半可能係router有一半可能係網路商既問題<br />\n唔好似為[熄router 再開返就得]一定係router問題<br />\n的確有機會係router老化左就壞會咁<br />\n但都有可能係機摟老化左連線一段時間就當Q左<br />\n你重開router,即係重新再連接過機摟佢又行到陣<br />\n網路商既問題佢地完全唔會認<br />\n明顯過左咁多年D野會壞<br />\n佢地死都唔認又老屈係你router問題<br />\n是但整隻電腦ONLINE GAME唔用router接直線放一晚<br />\n起身斷左你就知咩事<br />\n最好星期六試特別易出事<br />\n<br />\n咩用用下Wifi轉左4G果D都係咁因為電話有開補助<br />\n原因係為左比你好體驗佢檢查到你連出街唔穩定就會自動轉4G<br />\n <br />\nPS:買個好D既router都係會少左擔心佢出事,但網路商既問題最煩但又冇解,轉第2間都未必會好"},{"pid":"18625dc5eedce16f02b5dd1099dbaca0d46b3fa5","tid":805503,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"又係用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a759f08cbe67c24be9bb16ffe2c32beeff4ffd3","tid":805503,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"344ca3c4c85d1c6baee1f8ee7589bc10e271240f","tid":805503,"uid":41037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:11:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca72fcb9f6d12d6924a75f979f0a4dede24983dc","tid":805503,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:16:10.000Z","msg":"router都整得壞手機wifi既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n唔怪得咁多弱智啦"},{"pid":"67909875bed0b5b70a35791c13d6dc4099d01118","tid":805503,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:26:03.000Z","msg":"其他 device 又無事, 係得 iphone 係咁, 根本iPhone 設計缺憾"},{"pid":"ca0bbc8a34f1b7cab87df01e822769fc21dedcfa","tid":805503,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c092f4f61ccfd6c923f8d6f5601366e7c2e5e88","tid":805503,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 用緊Airport extreme都會有時上唔到 要係電話off一下wifi再開返先上到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f9ef380fe17515b6bad9978891230b8af180bb","tid":805503,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbe0e4cd199cbb759027f811467fbb39ad61381d","tid":805503,"uid":194130,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,